    <title>Git常用命令</title>
    <link href="https://tao1236.github.io/myBlog/2022/09/13/Git%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/"/>
    <id>https://tao1236.github.io/myBlog/2022/09/13/Git%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</id>
    <published>2022-09-13T14:36:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-09-13T14:05:44.790Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="排除监视文件"><a href="#排除监视文件" class="headerlink" title="排除监视文件"></a>排除监视文件</h2><p>在代码库根目录添加一个.gitignore文件，在文件中写上文件名（含路径）或路径名即可</p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="新建"><a href="#新建" class="headerlink" title="新建"></a>新建</h2><p>新建一个代码库</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git init &lt;repo&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>克隆一个项目</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git <span class="built_in">clone</span> [url]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h2><p>显示当前配置</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git config --list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编辑配置文件</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git config -e &lt;--global&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设置用户信息</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git config &lt;--global&gt; user.name <span class="string">&quot;[name]&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">$ git config &lt;--global&gt; user.email <span class="string">&quot;[email]&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="添加-x2F-提交"><a href="#添加-x2F-提交" class="headerlink" title="添加&#x2F;提交"></a>添加&#x2F;提交</h2><p>添加指定文件到暂存区</p><figure class="highlight gams"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">$</span> git add [<span class="keyword">file</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>添加指定目录到暂存区，包含子目录</p><figure class="highlight dockerfile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git <span class="keyword">add</span><span class="language-bash"> [<span class="built_in">dir</span>]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>添加当前目录的所有文件到暂存区</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git <span class="built_in">add</span> .</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将暂存区内容添加到本地仓库</p><figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">git</span> commit -m<span class="meta"> [message]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将本地的分支版本上传到远程并合并</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git push <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">远程主机名</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">本地分支名</span>&gt;</span>:<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">远程分支名</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果本地分支名与远程分支名相同，则可以省略冒号：</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git push <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">远程主机名</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">本地分支名</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;h2 id=&quot;排除监视文件&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#排除监视文件&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;排除监视文件&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;排除监视文件&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;在代码库根目录添加一个.gitignore文件，在文件中写上文件名（含路径）或路径名即可&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    
